# Pair interactions require lists of neighbours to be calculated
neighbor 2.0 bin
neigh_modify every 1 delay 0 check yes

fix Basepairs all property/atom i_idc ghost yes
read_data data.dsring2 fix Basepairs NULL Basepairs
